<br>
Target self and activate surgery clinic.  Target other player and continue to activate surgery clinic as much as needed.  I don't know if you can activate it more than once while targetting the same person as I never have needed more than two boosts.  If so, just try targetting a third person, or try switching between yourself and the other person each activation of the surgery clinic.  One is bound to work.<br>
<br>
